## 🚨 Emergency Override Protocol

**ONLY if critical project need:**

1. User MUST explicitly state: "OVERRIDE RULE [rule_id] for [reason]"
2. Document override in code comments
3. Create GitHub issue to track technical debt
4. Set reminder to fix in next sprint

